      "description": "With over 15 years of experience in various industries including energy, aerospace, metallurgy, banking, marketing, and HR, I am a software professional who specialises in TDD, clean code, and distributed systems. Throughout these years, I actively contributed to the definition and implementation of distributed systems that required high availability. Therefore, developing effective communication strategies (asynchronous vs synchronous) and comprehensive testing approaches were imperative.\n\n I am passionate about helping companies create maintainable products that align with their clients' needs. My focus is not only on implementation but also on the impact of the product, which includes empathising with clients and understanding their requirements to suggest improvements in product functionalities. I am proud of the positive impact I have made so far and always seek new challenges to learn and grow.\n\nMusic is another passion of mine, and I have been using my technical skills to showcase the power of technology in enhancing creativity and artistic expression. As an illustration, I have designed a unique project that applies Data Science to analyse and recommend the next chord to use in a song, making the songwriting process more efficient. This project has allowed me to explore the intersection of music and technology, and I am thrilled about the potential for future innovations in this field.\n\n",
